us.", "- Jeg kaller dem for englekoret. De har virkelig v\u00e6rt profesjonelle, sier han."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sortrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "3d4fb4d201cb427168eb108d2fc23eaf2941859e978a4b9f5990063a736bc28a"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-02-03T21:09:20.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Orkdalingen Nils Bredesen fikk fredag sjokkbeskjeden om at s\u00f8nnen var alvorlig skadd i en bilulykke ved Sarpsborg."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article7804543.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ulykkeMannfraOrkdal.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/b3b01dbb0a5f2169c608e32048bcee26cd66c0ee.jpg?597de440"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Det har ikke v\u00e6rt s\u00e5 lett \u00e5 v\u00e6re far -adressa.no", "- Helt forferdelig", "- Vanvittig flaks", "Profesjonelle pleiere"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "b3b01dbb0a5f2169c608e32048bcee26cd66c0ee"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["s\u00f8nnen", "alvorlig skadd"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["olavs hospital", "st. olavs hospital"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["sarpsborg", "oslo"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "nils bredesen"}, {"field": "kw-sentiment", "value": "negative"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article7804543.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ulykkeMannfraOrkda